<section class="philosophical-implications">
    <h2>Philosophical Perspectives</h2>

    <div class="nietzsche-section">
        <h3>Nietzsche's Void</h3>
        <div class="portrait-container">
            <img 
                src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/1b/Nietzsche187a.jpg"
                alt="Friedrich Nietzsche"
                class="philosopher-portrait"
            />
        </div>
        <div class="concept-animation">
            <div class="void-symbol"></div>
            <div class="meaning-creation"></div>
        </div>
        <p>
            Nietzsche's declaration "God is dead" represents more than religious skepticism; 
            it announces the collapse of all absolute values and meaning-giving structures. 
            In the face of cosmic meaninglessness, humans must become meaning-creators.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="cioran-section">
        <h3>Cioran's Nihilism</h3>
        <div class="portrait-container">
            <img 
                src="https://humanitas.ro/assets/images/authors/cioran.jpg"
                alt="Emil Cioran"
                class="philosopher-portrait"
            />
        </div>
        <div class="concept-animation">
            <div class="nihilism-symbol"></div>
        </div>
        <blockquote class="cioran-quote">
            "Viata-i eterica si funebra ca sinuciderea unui fluture."
        </blockquote>
        <p>
            Emil Cioran's radical nihilism suggests that consciousness itself is a cosmic 
            accident, making human existence both tragic and absurd. His philosophy 
            parallels quantum indeterminacy in its rejection of absolute meaning.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="implications-grid">
        <div class="implication-card">
            <h4>Quantum Meaninglessness</h4>
            <div class="animation-container">
                <div class="quantum-state"></div>
            </div>
            <p>
                The probabilistic nature of quantum mechanics suggests a universe 
                fundamentally devoid of deterministic meaning, echoing existentialist themes.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="implication-card">
            <h4>Creative Destruction</h4>
            <div class="animation-container">
                <div class="creation-destruction"></div>
            </div>
            <p>
                Like quantum fluctuations in the vacuum, meaning emerges from and returns 
                to nothingness in an eternal cycle of creation and destruction.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="implication-card">
            <h4>Cosmic Insignificance</h4>
            <div class="animation-container">
                <div class="cosmic-scale"></div>
            </div>
            <p>
                The vast scale of the universe and its quantum origins highlight human 
                insignificance while paradoxically empowering us as meaning-makers.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .philosophical-implications {
        margin: 4rem 0;
        padding: 2rem;
        background: rgba(var(--accent-dark), 0.2);
        border-radius: 12px;
    }

    h2, h3 {
        text-align: center;
        color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .portrait-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .philosopher-portrait {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        object-fit: cover;
        border: 4px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.3);
    }

    .cioran-quote {
        text-align: center;
        font-style: italic;
        color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        margin: 2rem 0;
        font-size: 1.2em;
        padding: 1rem;
        background: rgba(var(--accent-dark), 0.3);
        border-radius: 8px;
        border-left: 4px solid rgb(var(--accent-light));
    }

    .concept-animation {
        height: 150px;
        margin: 2rem 0;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .void-symbol {
        position: absolute;
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        border-radius: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        animation: voidPulse 4s infinite;
    }

    .meaning-creation {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: radial-gradient(
            circle at center,
            rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.2) 0%,
            transparent 70%
        );
        animation: meaningWave 6s infinite;
    }

    .nihilism-symbol {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 2px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        top: 50%;
        transform: translateY(-50%);
        animation: nihilismWave 3s infinite;
    }

    .implications-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    .implication-card {
        padding: 1.5rem;
        background: rgba(var(--accent-dark), 0.3);
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.2);
    }

    .implication-card h4 {
        color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .animation-container {
        height: 150px;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .quantum-state {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        border-radius: 50%;
        position: absolute;
        left: 50%;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        animation: quantumFluctuation 3s infinite;
    }

    .creation-destruction {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg,
            transparent,
            rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.3),
            transparent
        );
        animation: creationCycle 4s infinite;
    }

    .cosmic-scale {
        position: absolute;
        width: 2px;
        height: 2px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        left: 50%;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        animation: cosmicExpansion 5s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes voidPulse {
        0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0.8); opacity: 0.5; }
        50% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.2); opacity: 0.8; }
    }

    @keyframes meaningWave {
        0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.2; }
        50% { transform: scale(1.5); opacity: 0.4; }
    }

    @keyframes nihilismWave {
        0% { transform: translateY(-50%) scaleX(0.5); }
        50% { transform: translateY(-50%) scaleX(1.5); }
        100% { transform: translateY(-50%) scaleX(0.5); }
    }

    @keyframes quantumFluctuation {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 0; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0); }
        50% { opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); }
    }

    @keyframes creationCycle {
        0% { transform: translateX(-100%) scaleY(0.5); }
        50% { transform: translateX(0%) scaleY(1); }
        100% { transform: translateX(100%) scaleY(0.5); }
    }

    @keyframes cosmicExpansion {
        0% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); }
        100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(100); opacity: 0; }
    }
</style>